cURL command: curl -X POST http://localhost:5000/register -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"username":"testuser","password":"testpass"}'

Output:
{"message":"User successfully registered. Now you can login"}

---

Testing duplicate username:
cURL command: curl -X POST http://localhost:5000/register -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"username":"testuser","password":"testpass2"}'

Output:
{"message":"Username already exists"}

---

Testing missing password:
cURL command: curl -X POST http://localhost:5000/register -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"username":"newuser"}'

Output:
{"message":"Username and password are required"}
